@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### Teste de Endpoints - Helpdesk API
### Roteiro de validacao manual (tambem executado via npm test)

### 1. GET /health - Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. GET /users - Listar todos os usuarios
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

### 3. GET /tickets/summary - Resumo de tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets/summary

### 4. GET /tickets - Listar tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets

### 4.1 GET /tickets - Filtro por status
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets?status=open

### 4.2 GET /tickets - Filtro por categoria
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets?category=infra

### 4.3 GET /tickets - Busca por texto
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets?search=urgente

### 5. POST /tickets - Criar ticket
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Servidor down",
  "description": "O servidor de producao esta offline e urgente",
  "category": "infra",
  "requesterId": "user_ana"
}

### 6. GET /tickets/:id - Obter detalhes do ticket
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets/ticket_001

### 7. PATCH /tickets/:id/status - Atualizar status do ticket
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tickets/ticket_002/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "in_progress",
  "comment": "Comecando a investigar o problema",
  "authorId": "user_carla"
}

### 8. PATCH /tickets/:id/status - Fechar ticket com comentario obrigatorio
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tickets/ticket_002/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "closed",
  "comment": "Problema resolvido. Servidor reiniciado.",
  "authorId": "user_carla"
}

### 9. POST /tickets/:id/comments - Adicionar comentario
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets/ticket_001/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Adicionando mais detalhes sobre a solucao",
  "authorId": "user_bruno"
}

### 10. Testes de Erro - GET /tickets/:id com ID invalido
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets/invalid_id

### 11. Testes de Erro - POST /tickets sem campos obrigatorios
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Ticket incompleto"
}

### 12. Testes de Erro - POST /tickets com solicitante invalido
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Ticket teste",
  "description": "Descricao teste",
  "category": "sistemas",
  "requesterId": "user_inexistente"
}

### 13. Testes de Erro - PATCH /tickets/:id/status com status invalido
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tickets/ticket_001/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "invalid_status",
  "comment": "teste"
}

### 14. Testes de Erro - PATCH /tickets/:id/status fechar sem comentario
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tickets/ticket_001/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "closed"
}

### 15. Testes de Erro - POST /tickets/:id/comments sem campos obrigatorios
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets/ticket_001/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Apenas mensagem sem autor"
}
